在新国家政体时期，当时的公共教育部成立的头三年，共有四名不同的部长。<ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|last=Braga|first=Paulo Drumond|date=2010|title=Os Ministros da Educação Nacional (1936-1974): Sociologia de uma Função|url=http://www.scielo.mec.pt/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract&pid=S1645-72502010000200003&lng=pt&nrm=iso&tlng=en|journal=Revista Lusófona de Educação|issue=16|pages=23–38|issn=1645-7250|access-date=2020-12-26|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731022842/http://www.scielo.mec.pt/scielo.php?script=sci_abstract&pid=S1645-72502010000200003&lng=pt&nrm=iso&tlng=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>
